27:06.000 --> 27:10.000
A company can start to rest on laurels.

27:10.000 --> 27:14.000
I already have a stable position on the market,

27:14.000 --> 27:16.000
I already have a stable demand,

27:16.000 --> 27:19.000
I already have a huge number of consumers,

27:19.000 --> 27:26.000
and, accordingly, I can slightly weaken my activity,

27:26.000 --> 27:29.000
because I already have certain achievements.

27:30.000 --> 27:34.000
This is the so-called state of comfort.

27:34.000 --> 27:39.000
The company experiences, the company owners, the company employees,

27:39.000 --> 27:43.000
those who strive to come to work in this company

27:43.000 --> 27:45.000
precisely in order to touch these myths,

27:45.000 --> 27:47.000
to become part of these myths,

27:47.000 --> 27:51.000
they are in a state of comfort,

27:51.000 --> 27:54.000
