28:11.000 --> 28:14.000
the number of advertisements is increasing,

28:14.000 --> 28:19.000
competitors that have emerged are dumping prices,

28:19.000 --> 28:24.000
and, accordingly, they are taking away the markets that we have already conquered.

28:24.000 --> 28:27.000
This comfort is what leads to stagnation,

28:27.000 --> 28:29.000
what leads to stagnation,

28:29.000 --> 28:32.000
and, accordingly, from this state of comfort,

28:32.000 --> 28:36.000
you need to leave for further development,

28:36.000 --> 28:39.000
for further organizational changes.

28:39.000 --> 28:41.000
This will make it harder,

28:41.000 --> 28:44.000
because the company has a history,

28:44.000 --> 28:46.000
the company has experience,

28:46.000 --> 28:50.000
the company has traditions that have proven its success,

28:50.000 --> 28:53.000
but, on the other hand,

28:53.000 --> 28:57.000
these conditions, these successes, these traditions

28:57.000 --> 29:01.000
