30:42.000 --> 30:45.000
to go back to the normal working day,

30:45.000 --> 30:49.000
to look at the changes again,

30:49.000 --> 30:51.000
the returns that we get,

30:51.000 --> 30:55.000
in order to either develop further

30:55.000 --> 30:58.000
and create new myths,

30:58.000 --> 31:00.000
achieve new successes,

31:00.000 --> 31:02.000
achieve new results,

