33:51.000 --> 33:54.000
First of all, the growth of the organization,

33:54.000 --> 33:56.000
the achievements that the organization receives

33:56.000 --> 33:58.000
as a result of its development,

33:58.000 --> 34:01.000
and the time that is required for this growth.

34:01.000 --> 34:07.000
The Grainer highlights five main phases of growth,

34:07.000 --> 34:11.000
and as for these phases of growth,

34:11.000 --> 34:14.000
