34:14.000 --> 34:17.000
The first phase is the creative growth phase.

34:17.000 --> 34:20.000
The organization enters the market,

34:20.000 --> 34:24.000
it takes its place under the sun,

34:24.000 --> 34:30.000
it searches for goods and services

34:30.000 --> 34:34.000
that are in demand by consumers,

34:34.000 --> 34:39.000
