34:39.000 --> 34:45.000
This is the stage of the hard work on the Danka model,

34:45.000 --> 34:47.000
which we have already discussed.

34:49.000 --> 34:53.000
If this stage is successfully overcome,

34:53.000 --> 34:56.000
that is, we find what to produce,

34:56.000 --> 35:00.000
what will be in demand,

35:00.000 --> 35:05.000
if we understand what services will be in demand,

35:05.000 --> 35:08.000
then the organization begins to develop,

35:08.000 --> 35:10.000
the organization begins to make a profit,

35:10.000 --> 35:14.000
and this is where the first crisis of leadership comes.

35:16.000 --> 35:19.000
Usually, an organization is created by people,

35:19.000 --> 35:21.000
and if the organization is small,

35:21.000 --> 35:26.000
