35:26.000 --> 35:31.000
all people make the same big contribution to the development of the organization.

35:31.000 --> 35:36.000
The organization has achieved some results and is expanding.

35:36.000 --> 35:40.000
New employees appear, new structures appear,

35:40.000 --> 35:46.000
and now there is not necessarily a constant fight,

35:46.000 --> 35:51.000
but an unanimous struggle between the founders,

35:51.000 --> 35:53.000
between the founders,

35:53.000 --> 35:56.000
between the owners of the company,

35:56.000 --> 36:03.000
who contributed the most to the organization's development,

36:03.000 --> 36:09.000
how should the profits and dividends be distributed between them,

36:09.000 --> 36:15.000
and who will determine the path of the company's development.

36:15.000 --> 36:19.000
Who will then make, control,

36:19.000 --> 36:24.000
launch the plan of organizational development, organizational change,

36:24.000 --> 36:26.000
because all people are different,

36:26.000 --> 36:29.000
and there is not always agreement between them

36:30.000 --> 36:34.000
