37:03.000 --> 37:08.000
of the changes that will be made.

37:08.000 --> 37:12.000
If this crisis of leadership is not overcome,

37:12.000 --> 37:16.000
then it leads to the division of the company,

37:16.000 --> 37:21.000
it leads to the loss of the won positions,

37:21.000 --> 37:24.000
and, accordingly, in fact,

37:24.000 --> 37:28.000
other smaller companies may arise,

37:28.000 --> 37:31.000
separated from the original company,

37:31.000 --> 37:34.000
