37:44.000 --> 37:46.000
when the owners, the managers,

37:46.000 --> 37:49.000
when those people who were originally in the company

37:49.000 --> 37:52.000
agree among themselves how to develop,

37:52.000 --> 37:55.000
agree with you about the sphere of responsibility,

37:55.000 --> 37:58.000
share their powers, delegate their powers,

37:58.000 --> 38:01.000
delegate the sphere of responsibility that they have,

38:01.000 --> 38:06.000
then the next stage of organizational growth,

38:06.000 --> 38:10.000
the stage of directed growth, comes.

38:10.000 --> 38:13.000
We agreed on a strategy,

38:13.000 --> 38:17.000
we agreed on who is responsible for which element of this strategy,

38:17.000 --> 38:20.000
we developed a plan,

38:20.000 --> 38:23.000
we reached an agreement inside,

38:23.000 --> 38:26.000
