38:26.000 --> 38:29.000
We see the end goals,

38:29.000 --> 38:32.000
we know how to move towards these goals,

38:32.000 --> 38:35.000
and we begin to invest funds for further movement.

38:35.000 --> 38:40.000
Again, there are both positive and negative moments.

38:40.000 --> 38:43.000
The positive moment is that

38:43.000 --> 38:46.000
there is a constant control of feedback,

38:46.000 --> 38:49.000
which is being developed in order to achieve

38:49.000 --> 38:52.000
more economic results,

38:52.000 --> 38:56.000
strengthen, improve its place in the market,

38:56.000 --> 39:00.000
