01:20:39.000 --> 01:20:42.000
with the leasing company

01:20:42.000 --> 01:20:45.000
that we are talking about.

01:20:45.000 --> 01:20:48.000
In this regard, the task of the

01:20:48.000 --> 01:20:51.000
fight for the market was set.

01:20:52.000 --> 01:20:55.000
It was not just about maintaining

01:20:55.000 --> 01:20:58.000
the existing results, not just about

01:20:58.000 --> 01:21:01.000
buying the existing profits, but

01:21:01.000 --> 01:21:04.000
also about increasing these profits.

01:21:04.000 --> 01:21:07.000
Different solutions were sought.

01:21:07.000 --> 01:21:10.000
There were two main ways.

01:21:10.000 --> 01:21:13.000
Some leasing companies thought that

01:21:13.000 --> 01:21:16.000
the problem was that we needed to increase

01:21:16.000 --> 01:21:19.000
the number of managers in the company

01:21:20.000 --> 01:21:23.000
who would use the already developed

01:21:23.000 --> 01:21:26.000
methods, the already recommended

01:21:26.000 --> 01:21:29.000
forms of signing leasing contracts.

01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:32.000
The more of them there were, the more

01:21:32.000 --> 01:21:35.000
we would increase the market segment.

01:21:35.000 --> 01:21:38.000
Unfortunately, this approach, this

01:21:38.000 --> 01:21:41.000
direction of development did not give

01:21:41.000 --> 01:21:44.000
the desired result.

01:21:44.000 --> 01:21:47.000
For example, there was a company

01:21:47.000 --> 01:21:50.000
that was very interested in buying

01:21:50.000 --> 01:21:53.000
new leasing products.

01:21:53.000 --> 01:21:56.000
For the simple reason that other

01:21:56.000 --> 01:21:59.000
leasing companies, especially foreign

01:21:59.000 --> 01:22:02.000
ones, were bringing new, more

01:22:02.000 --> 01:22:05.000
profitable contracts, new damping

01:22:05.000 --> 01:22:08.000
prices, new damping contracts.

01:22:08.000 --> 01:22:11.000
Accordingly, they were interested in

01:22:11.000 --> 01:22:14.000
conquering the new Russian market.

01:22:14.000 --> 01:22:17.000
They offered a large number of leasing

01:22:17.000 --> 01:22:20.000
products that turned out to be much

01:22:20.000 --> 01:22:23.000
more competitive than the ones our

01:22:23.000 --> 01:22:26.000
company had.

01:22:26.000 --> 01:22:29.000
In this regard, the adapters, consisting

01:22:29.000 --> 01:22:32.000
of those people who did not want to

01:22:32.000 --> 01:22:35.000
change the existing forms of contracts,

01:22:35.000 --> 01:22:38.000
existing terms of contracts, terms of

01:22:38.000 --> 01:22:41.000
agreements, could not bring to the

01:22:42.000 --> 01:22:45.000
positive results.

01:22:45.000 --> 01:22:48.000
And the leasing company very quickly

01:22:48.000 --> 01:22:51.000
lost not only the leading position,

01:22:51.000 --> 01:22:54.000
but also the invested funds, the

01:22:54.000 --> 01:22:57.000
client base, and gradually it began to

01:22:57.000 --> 01:23:00.000
lose the reputation it had.

01:23:00.000 --> 01:23:03.000
The situation changed after the

01:23:03.000 --> 01:23:06.000
company came to the Russian market.

01:23:06.000 --> 01:23:09.000
The company was in the process of

01:23:09.000 --> 01:23:12.000
changing its name.

01:23:12.000 --> 01:23:15.000
It was a company that understood that

01:23:15.000 --> 01:23:18.000
the transfer of already approved methods

01:23:18.000 --> 01:23:21.000
that were successful in 2005, 2006, and

01:23:21.000 --> 01:23:24.000
even in early 2007, did not bring the

01:23:24.000 --> 01:23:27.000
desired result.

01:23:27.000 --> 01:23:30.000
New competitive products, new

01:23:30.000 --> 01:23:33.000
leasing contracts, new leasing

01:23:33.000 --> 01:23:36.000
contracts, new leasing contracts,

01:23:36.000 --> 01:23:39.000
new leasing agreements, new leasing

01:23:39.000 --> 01:23:42.000
programs, which will be competitive

01:23:42.000 --> 01:23:45.000
compared to those products that

01:23:45.000 --> 01:23:48.000
entered the market by foreign companies.

01:23:48.000 --> 01:23:51.000
These were innovators who perfectly

01:23:51.000 --> 01:23:54.000
understood that in order to only

01:23:54.000 --> 01:23:57.000
return the early economic results,

01:23:57.000 --> 01:24:00.000
it would take some time.

01:24:00.000 --> 01:24:03.000
And this is what happened.

01:24:03.000 --> 01:24:06.000
There was no other way, because the

01:24:06.000 --> 01:24:09.000
old approaches carried out by the old

01:24:09.000 --> 01:24:12.000
management, and even by adaptive

01:24:12.000 --> 01:24:15.000
means, did not lead to the desired

01:24:15.000 --> 01:24:18.000
result.

01:24:18.000 --> 01:24:21.000
And after fundamentally new ideas

01:24:21.000 --> 01:24:24.000
were proposed, responsibilities were

01:24:24.000 --> 01:24:27.000
redistributed, new leasing contracts

01:24:27.000 --> 01:24:30.000
were created, and the company was

01:24:30.000 --> 01:24:33.000
able to return to the leading position.

01:24:33.000 --> 01:24:36.000
New divisions were created, new

01:24:36.000 --> 01:24:39.000
structures were created, the process of

01:24:39.000 --> 01:24:42.000
training managers was changed, the

01:24:42.000 --> 01:24:45.000
processes of rewarding managers were

01:24:45.000 --> 01:24:48.000
changed, the motivational scheme of

01:24:48.000 --> 01:24:51.000
managers was changed. By the end of the

01:24:51.000 --> 01:24:54.000
year, the situation began to change, and

01:24:54.000 --> 01:24:57.000
our leasing company gradually returned

01:24:57.000 --> 01:25:00.000
to the leading position. Of course, it

01:25:00.000 --> 01:25:03.000
could not fully play back the lost

01:25:03.000 --> 01:25:06.000
positions, but nevertheless, the results

01:25:06.000 --> 01:25:09.000
that were obtained allowed the company

01:25:09.000 --> 01:25:12.000
to exist further, and not to announce

01:25:12.000 --> 01:25:15.000
bankruptcy, which was the point.

01:25:15.000 --> 01:25:18.000
Here is the situation. If the innovators

01:25:18.000 --> 01:25:21.000
came and started to carry out this

01:25:21.000 --> 01:25:24.000
policy right away, maybe the results

01:25:25.000 --> 01:25:28.000
would be different. It is difficult to say,

01:25:28.000 --> 01:25:31.000
because only after the management

01:25:31.000 --> 01:25:34.000
of the company was convinced of the

01:25:34.000 --> 01:25:37.000
inadequacy, the inefficiency of the

01:25:37.000 --> 01:25:40.000
previously used means, it was forced to

01:25:40.000 --> 01:25:43.000
go for new significant investment

01:25:43.000 --> 01:25:46.000
and to replace the entire top management.

01:25:46.000 --> 01:25:49.000
This is, again, a painful process,

01:25:49.000 --> 01:25:52.000
and it is not easy to explain.

01:25:53.000 --> 01:25:56.000
However, in this case, we have achieved

01:25:56.000 --> 01:25:59.000
the results. Therefore, when we talk about

01:25:59.000 --> 01:26:02.000
innovators and adapters, the main

01:26:02.000 --> 01:26:05.000
criterion here is the timing of these

01:26:05.000 --> 01:26:08.000
changes, the presence of a plan of

01:26:08.000 --> 01:26:11.000
changes, the coordination of those

01:26:11.000 --> 01:26:14.000
indicators, which cannot be lowered,

01:26:14.000 --> 01:26:17.000
and the coordination of methods and

01:26:17.000 --> 01:26:20.000
means of investing the results that

01:26:20.000 --> 01:26:21.000
